---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { t } from '../i18n/ui';

const locale = 'en' as const;
---

<BaseLayout
  locale={locale}
  title="About"
  description="Iara Santos is an interior designer specializing in lighting design and project management, with a focus on residential and commercial work."
>
  <section class="about container">
    <header class="about-header">
      <p class="eyebrow" data-anim>About</p>
      <h1 class="display about-title" data-anim>
        A practice rooted in <em>material attention</em> and considered light.
      </h1>
    </header>

    <div class="about-body prose-container">
      <p class="lede">
        I'm Iara Santos — an architect from São Paulo, building a practice in
        interior design with lighting and project management as integral disciplines.
      </p>

      <p>
        My training is in architecture, my specialization in lighting design, and
        my method shaped by years of running complex projects on schedule and on budget.
        I believe the best interiors come from a single mind keeping all three threads
        pulled tight: the spatial idea, the material truth, and the lighting that lets
        both register.
      </p>

      <p>
        I work in residential at the high end and in commercial projects where
        atmosphere matters as much as program. I write here as a way of thinking out loud
        — about projects of my own, about work I admire, and about the unglamorous craft
        of getting beautiful things actually built.
      </p>

      <h2>Background</h2>

      <p>
        Architecture (Brazil). Specialized training in lighting design.
        Built and currently maintain ISSA Project, a project management application
        designed specifically for interior and lighting workflows.
      </p>

      <h2>Currently</h2>

      <p>
        Working remotely with clients across the Americas. Open to senior interior
        designer and lighting design roles with US-based studios — fully remote, with
        occasional travel.
      </p>

      <h2>Selected expertise</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>Residential, high-end (full design and documentation)</li>
        <li>Workplace and corporate interiors (mid-sized to enterprise floors)</li>
        <li>Layered architectural lighting (specification, controls, and color tuning)</li>
        <li>Project management for design teams (RFP through punch list)</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="about-actions">
        <a href="/cv-iara-santos.pdf" class="btn-ghost" download>
          {t(locale, 'about.cv')} →
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-ghost">
          Get in touch →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about { padding: 5rem 0 4rem; }
  .about-header {
    max-width: 50rem;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
  }
  .about-header .eyebrow { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .about-title {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .lede {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }

  .about-body p:first-of-type::first-letter {
    /* override drop cap só do prose normal — aqui já temos um lede */
    float: none;
    font-size: inherit;
    color: inherit;
    line-height: inherit;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-actions {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
</style>
